title: Have anyone seen this kind of "AND" symbols?
content:
look at the text between building & remodeling. you will see text "and" with some artistic design. I have seen this text used in other designs also. can someone guide me what is it & where i can find clear image of this?

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20100331041117im_/http:/typophile.com/files/1022089W_5896.jpg)
author: artslons

comments.content:
I included a large compliment of catchwords in Phaeton (including two version of AND visible in the linked specimen).  
\> [Specimen at Veer](http://web.archive.org/web/20100331041117/http:/www.veer.com/products/typedetail.aspx?image=UMT0000447)  
\> [Specimen at Aquatoad](http://web.archive.org/web/20100331041117/http:/www.aquatoad.com/portfolio.php?section_id=3&subsection_id=5&portfolio_id=29)
